From fceed4d441debbf1248e9a03a559c1b3e886080f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: YHR <yinmacau345@gmail.com>
Date: Fri, 15 May 2026 12:15:14 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] @ fix: separate edit mode from defaults, optimize validation
 performance
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

修改模式 now controls whether apply uses template defaults (OFF) or
user-edited settings (ON). Saved settings are reloaded only when edit
mode is activated, and "重置为默认" clears persisted state.

Format validation optimized: pre-computed XML namespace constants,
direct child element lookup instead of subtree search, throttled
progress updates to prevent Tkinter GUI freeze on large documents,
and added ensure_docx for .doc file support.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>
